  "body": "# Problem\r\n\r\nKeycard applet installation takes ~20 seconds. During the process we only show spinning circle indicator so it's not clear how much time left.\r\n\r\n# Implementation\r\n\r\nWe could show progress bar or percentage number. \r\n\r\nInstaller could emit events to status-react signaling the step it's currently on.\r\n\r\n# Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nShow progress bar or percentage number during applet installation.\r\n\r\n# Notes\r\nInstaller code\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/react-native-status-keycard/blob/master/android/src/main/java/im/status/ethereum/keycard/Installer.java#L38 \r\n\r\nEmit events example https://github.com/status-im/react-native-status-keycard/blob/master/android/src/main/java/im/status/ethereum/keycard/SmartCard.java#L112\r\n\n\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/11767950?s=400&v=4\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div><img src=\"https://assets-cdn.github.com/favicon.ico\" height=\"14\"> GitHub</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/status-im/react-native-status-keycard\">status-im/react-native-status-keycard</a></strong></div><div>Contribute to status-im/react-native-status-keycard development by creating an account on GitHub.</div></blockquote>\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/11767950?s=400&v=4\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div><img src=\"https://assets-cdn.github.com/favicon.ico\" height=\"14\"> GitHub</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/status-im/react-native-status-keycard\">status-im/react-native-status-keycard</a></strong></div><div>Contribute to status-im/react-native-status-keycard development by creating an account on GitHub.</div></blockquote>",
